title: [Crown and Kettle, Trinkets]
description: An oversized frame of copper-lacquered wood encircles a wrought pewter rack across the back wall, the display presented before a brushed grey velvet-padded chaise in the center of the room.  A crown-shaped teal iron stove and accompanying plum wicker basket are set upon a rounded haon table, flanked by numerous sketchings of charcoal and ink.
